            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1621936824239-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the aubergines are cooking, peel the <strong>brown</strong> <strong>onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>and chop very roughly</p><p>Peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and chop the <strong>ginger </strong>and<strong> garlic </strong>roughly</p><p>Separate the<strong> coriander leaves</strong> from their <strong>stalks</strong> and set them aside</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1621936834666-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1621936834666-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1621936834666-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1621936834666-x1000.jpg",
