          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-2-1621936834666-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>onion</strong>, <strong>ginger</strong>, <strong>garlic</strong>, <strong>cayenne pepper</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!), <strong>curry powder</strong> and <strong>coriander stalks</strong> (reserve the leaves for garnish!) to a <strong>food processor</strong></p><p>Blitz until smooth or very finely chopped – this is your <strong>Sri Lankan-style curry paste</strong></p><p>Tip: No food processor? Chop everything up as finely as you can and mix it together!</p>",
